## ğŸ› ï¸ Development

### Generate New Module

```bash
# Generate a complete DDD module (aggregate + events + repository + use case + tests)
/path/to/bento/bin/bento-gen gen module Product \
  --fields "name:str,price:float,stock:int" \
  --output .

# Generate individual components
/path/to/bento/bin/bento-gen gen usecase UpdateProduct --output .
/path/to/bento/bin/bento-gen gen event ProductDeactivated --output .
```

### Run Tests

```bash
# Run all tests
pytest

# Run unit tests only
pytest -m unit

# Run with coverage
pytest --cov --cov-report=html

# Run specific test file
pytest tests/unit/domain/test_product.py
```

### Code Quality

```bash
# Format code
ruff format .

# Lint code
ruff check .

# Type check
mypy .
```

